"{\n  \"correct\": \"no\",\n  \"explanation\": \"The code is using lmplot with FacetGrid which is incorrect. According to the seaborn documentation, lmplot is a figure-level function that combines regplot and FacetGrid. Therefore, it should not be used with FacetGrid. Instead, regplot should be used with FacetGrid.\",\n  \"patch\": \"5c5\\n< g = sns.FacetGrid(data=tips, col='time', row='sex')\\n---\\n> g = sns.FacetGrid(data=tips, col='time', row='sex')\\n6c6\\n< g.map(sns.lmplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n---\\n> g.map(sns.regplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n\"\n}"